// Man page for uptime
manUptime="UPTIME(7)                        X Shell Manual                        UPTIME(7)

<b>NAME</b>
    uptime - Display x session uptime
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>uptime</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Display the current x session uptime showing how long
    the x environment has been running.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>uptime</b>
    Show x session uptime"